istory on every model call if practical.\\n\\n## Notes\\n\\nDo not rely on the browser alone as the source of truth.\\n\\n## Suggested commit label\\n\\n`feat(prompt-34): ui events to agent context`\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nprompts/34-ui-events-to-agent-context.yolopilot.jsonlines:7:{\"color\": \"cyan\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83d\\udee0\\ufe0f\", \"event_type\": \"Command Started\", \"message\": \"in progress: /bin/zsh -lc 'rg -n \\\"session snapshot|context summary|event log|ui event|regenerat|snapshot|agent context|rolling context|chat summary|workflow stage|session event|session_snapshot|context_summary\\\" backend frontend docs -S'\", \"raw_event\": {\"item\": {\"aggregated_output\": \"\", \"command\": \"/bin/zsh -lc 'rg -n \\\"session snapshot|context summary|event log|ui event|regenerat|snapshot|agent context|rolling context|chat summary|workflow stage|session event|session_snapshot|context_summary\\\" backend frontend docs -S'\", \"exit_code\": null, \"id\": \"item_1\", \"status\": \"in_progress\", \"type\": \"command_execution\"}, \"type\": \"item.started\"}, \"task_display_context\": {\"event_number\": 7, \"prompt_index\": 35, \"prompt_name\": \"34 \\u2014 Send UI Events Back Into Agent Context\", \"prompt_total\": 100}, \"timestap\": \"2026-04-01T05:55:55-07:00\"}\nprompts/34-ui-events-to-agent-context.yolopilot.jsonlines:9:{\"color\": \"cyan\", \"emoji\": \"\\ud83d\\udee0\\ufe0f\", \"event_type\": \"Command Finished\", \"message\": \"completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc 'rg -n \\\"session snapshot|context summary|event log|ui event|regenerat|snapshot|agent context|rolling context|chat summary|workflow stage|session event|session_snapshot|context_summary\\\" backend frontend docs -S'\", \"raw_event\": {\"item\": {\"aggregated_output\": \"frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx:7:  type SessionSnapshot,\\nfrontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx:15:  useSessionCurrentSnapshot,\\nfrontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspac